OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fcloudy, with this thickening overnight
OL,7,Fto produce hill fog by the early hours
OL,8,Fof Tuesday. A few light showers
OL,9,Fpossible. A warm and rather muggy
OL,10,Fnight under the blanket of cloud with
OL,11,Flight winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud lifting to
OL,14,Fallow some bright or sunny spells to
OL,15,Femerge for a time. Dry to begin, but
OL,16,Frain arriving to end the day. Warm and
OL,17,Fhumid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
