OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FRain
OL,6,Fpossible on Wednesday. Otherwise,
OL,7,Fmostly dry with some warm spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine, though this often turning
OL,9,Fhazy under variable amounts of cloud.
OL,10,FRemaining humid.
